snippet.title: Slam Tilt gameplay (PC Game, 1996)
snippet.description:
Gameplay for Slam Tilt, PC game produced by Robert Epps in 1996 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/slam-tilt/1840/
Playing through all the tables of this nice pinball simulation and making many points.
Played through emulated Windows (Win 98/Win XP) virtual machine.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Pinball Dreams - https://youtu.be/zGI-VvMZqCE
Extreme Pinball - https://youtu.be/R6ipdCCZBYs
